Minimal Unix domain sockets client-server example

Build and run:
./build.sh

./server
./client

client> sent 3 bytes: 123
server> received 3 bytes: 123
server> sent 3 bytes: 456
client> received 3 bytes: 456

Relevant manpages:
- man 3 socket
- man 7 unix
- man 0 sys_un.h
- man 3 bind
- man 3 listen
- man 3 accept
- man 3 recv
- man 3 send
